I"<p>Welcome to the Belongie Lab website! Our lab carries out research in Computer Vision and Machine Learning, exploring problem areas including fine-grained analysis of multimodal data, self-supervised learning, 2D/3D generative models, and augmented reality.</p>

<p>Belongie Lab is founded and led by Prof. <a href="https://scholar.google.com/citations?user=ORr4XJYAAAAJ&amp;hl=zh-CN">Serge Belongie</a>. Belongie Lab has members and alumni in <a href="https://ucsd.edu/">UCSD</a> (2001 - 2012), <a href="https://www.cornell.edu/">Cornell</a> and <a href="https://www.tech.cornell.edu/">Cornell Tech</a> (2013 - 2021) and <a href="https://www.ku.dk/english/">University of Copenhagen</a> (2021 - present).</p>

